msgid "Lebih dari Sekadar Pesan Anonim"
msgstr "More than Just Anonymous Messages"

msgid ""
"CurhatBox dirancang menggunakan teknologi Web terkini untuk menghadirkan pengalaman komunikasi jujur\n"
"                    yang <strong class=\"text-white\">Aman</strong>, <strong class=\"text-white\">Estetik</strong>, dan <strong class=\"text-white\">Penuh Kendali</strong>."
msgstr ""
"CurhatBox is designed using the latest Web technology to deliver an honest "
"communication experience that is <strong class=\"text-"
"white\">Secure</strong>, <strong class=\"text-white\">Aesthetic</strong>, "
"and <strong class=\"text-white\">Full of Control</strong>."

msgid "Format IG Story Instan"
msgstr "Instant IG Story Format"

msgid ""
"Ubah pesan jujur dan balasanmu menjadi gambar estetik beresolusi tinggi yang"
" siap dipamerkan di Instagram Story hanya dengan satu klik."
msgstr ""
"Change your honest messages and replies into high-resolution aesthetic "
"images ready to be showcased on Instagram Story with just one click."

msgid "Analitik Penggemar"
msgstr "Fan Analytics"

msgid ""
"Pantau performa profilmu dengan dasbor analitik visual. Lihat grafik tren "
"pesan harian, jam sibuk, dan analisis sentimen emoji audiens."
msgstr ""
"Monitor your profile performance with a visual analytics dashboard. See "
"graphs of daily message trends, busy hours, and audience emoji sentiment "
"analysis."

msgid "Kustomisasi Premium"
msgstr "Premium Customization"

msgid ""
"Ekspresikan dirimu sesungguhnya! Unggah foto Avatar dan pilih warna Tema "
"sesuka hati untuk menghiasi halaman publikmu."
msgstr ""
"Express your true self! Upload an Avatar photo and choose a Theme color as "
"you like to decorate your public page."

msgid "Mode Anti-Jejak (Self-Destruct)"
msgstr "Anti-Trace Mode (Self-Destruct)"

#| msgid ""
#| "Takut rahasia terbongkar? Kirim pesan dengan Mode Sekali Baca. Pesan akan dihapus secara\n"
#| "                                permanen dari server <strong class=\"text-white\">sesaat setelah penerima membukanya</strong>. Bebas jejak digital seutuhnya."
msgid ""
"Takut rahasia terbongkar? Kirim pesan dengan Mode Sekali Baca. Pesan akan dihapus secara\n"
"                                permanen dari server <strong class=\"text-body\">sesaat setelah penerima membukanya</strong>. Bebas jejak digital seutuhnya."
msgstr ""
"Fear secrets being uncovered? Send a message with Single Read Mode. The "
"message will be permanently deleted from the server <strong class=\"text-"
"body\">as soon as the recipient opens it</strong>. Fully free from digital "
"traces."

msgid "Keamanan Siber Proaktif"
msgstr "Proactive Cyber Security"

msgid ""
"Anti perundungan! CurhatBox mendeteksi kata-kata kasar dan mencatat <strong "
"class=\"text-body\">Petunjuk Lingkungan Pengirim (Browser/OS)</strong>. "
"Sebagai penerima, Anda memiliki kendali penuh untuk memblokir penyerang "
"selamanya."
msgstr ""
"Anti-bullying! CurhatBox detects rude words and records <strong "
"class=\"text-body\">Sender Environment Hints (Browser/OS)</strong>. As a "
"recipient, you have full control to block attackers forever."

msgid "Filosofi Kejujuran Digital"
msgstr "Digital Honesty Philosophy"

msgid ""
"CurhatBox lahir dari sebuah keresahan sederhana: di dunia yang semakin "
"terkoneksi secara digital, ruang untuk berbicara jujur tanpa penghakiman "
"justru semakin sempit. Kami percaya bahwa setiap individu membutuhkan \\"
msgstr ""
"CurhatBox was born from a simple concern: in an increasingly digitally "
"connected world, the space for talking honestly without judgment is "
"narrowing. We believe that every individual needs a \"secret box\" where "
"they can receive pure feedback, criticism, or appreciation without being "
"limited by social identity boundaries."

msgid ""
"Namun, kejujuran tidak boleh menjadi alasan untuk kebencian. Itulah sebabnya"
" CurhatBox tidak hanya sekadar menyediakan fitur anonimitas, tetapi juga "
"membangun ekosistem yang aman. Kami menggunakan algoritma pemrosesan bahasa "
"alami (NLP) sederhana untuk memfilter konten negatif dan memberikan kendali "
"penuh kepada pemilik profil untuk moderasi mandiri."
msgstr ""
"However, honesty should not be an excuse for hatred. That is why CurhatBox "
"does not only provide anonymity features, but also builds a safe ecosystem. "
"We use simple natural language processing (NLP) algorithms to filter "
"negative content and give full control to profile owners for self-"
"moderation."

msgid "Visi & Misi Kami"
msgstr "Our Vision & Mission"

msgid ""
"Visi kami adalah menjadi platform komunikasi anonim nomor satu yang paling "
"dipercaya dan aman di Indonesia. Kami ingin menghapus stigma bahwa "
"anonimitas selalu berujung pada hal negatif. Dengan fitur edukasi dan "
"moderasi yang tepat, kami percaya anonimitas dapat menjadi katalisator bagi "
"pertumbuhan diri dan perbaikan hubungan sosial."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Misi kami mencakup tiga pilar utama: Keamanan Data, Kenyamanan Pengguna, dan"
" Inovasi Fitur. Kami terus berusaha untuk melakukan enkripsi data yang lebih"
" kuat, antarmuka yang lebih intuitif, dan fitur-fitur seru seperti analitik "
"pesan dan integrasi media sosial yang memudahkan pengguna untuk berbagi "
"kebahagiaan mereka."
msgstr ""
"Our mission encompasses three main pillars: Data Security, User Comfort, and"
" Feature Innovation. We continue to strive for stronger data encryption, a "
"more intuitive interface, and fun features like message analytics and social"
" media integration that make it easier for users to share their happiness."

#| msgid "Kebijakan Privasi - CurhatBox"
msgid "Kenapa Harus CurhatBox?"
msgstr "Why Choose CurhatBox?"

msgid ""
"Berbeda dengan platform pesan anonim lainnya yang seringkali menjadi sarang "
"spam dan kebencian, CurhatBox menyeimbangkan antara privasi pengirim dan "
"perlindungan penerima. Fitur 'Sender Hints' kami memberikan informasi "
"minimal namun sangat berguna bagi penerima untuk mengenali konteks pesan "
"tanpa membongkar identitas pengirim. Ini adalah titik tengah yang kami "
"ciptakan demi kenyamanan bersama."
msgstr ""
"Unlike other anonymous messaging platforms that are often nests for spam and"
" hatred, CurhatBox balances sender privacy and recipient protection. Our "
"'Sender Hints' feature provides minimal but very useful information for the "
"recipient to recognize the context of the message without uncovering the "
"sender's identity. This is the middle ground we created for mutual comfort."

msgid "Teknologi di Balik Layar"
msgstr "Technology Behind the Scenes"

msgid ""
"Untuk menghadirkan pengalaman yang mulus dan cepat, CurhatBox dibangun di "
"atas tumpukan teknologi modern yang tangguh:"
msgstr ""
"To deliver a seamless and fast experience, CurhatBox is built on a robust "
"stack of modern technology:"

msgid ""
"<li><strong>Python & Django:</strong> Framework web tingkat tinggi yang "
"menjamin keamanan data dan kecepatan pengembangan.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>Python & Django:</strong> High-level web framework that ensures "
"data security and development speed.</li>"

msgid ""
"<li><strong>Daphne & WebSockets:</strong> Memungkinkan pengiriman pesan "
"secara real-time tanpa perlu memuat ulang halaman.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>Daphne & WebSockets:</strong> Enables real-time message delivery"
" without the need to reload the page.</li>"

msgid ""
"<li><strong>PostgreSQL:</strong> Sistem manajemen basis data relasional yang"
" memastikan integritas dan keamanan data ceritamu.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>PostgreSQL:</strong> Relational database management system that "
"ensures the integrity and security of your story data.</li>"

msgid ""
"<li><strong>Redis:</strong> Digunakan untuk menangani antrean data dan "
"caching agar performa situs tetap responsif meski dalam trafik tinggi.</li>"
msgstr ""
"<li><strong>Redis:</strong> Used to handle data queues and caching so that "
"site performance remains responsive even in high traffic.</li>"

