#| msgid "Kebijakan Privasi"
msgid "I. Keamanan & Privasi"
msgstr "I. Security & Privacy"

#| msgid "Apakah CurhatBox benar-benar anonim?"
msgid "Apakah data saya benar-benar aman dan terenkripsi?"
msgstr "Is my data truly secure and encrypted?"

msgid ""
"Keamanan adalah fondasi utama CurhatBox. Kami menggunakan protokol enkripsi "
"tingkat lanjut untuk memastikan bahwa pesan Anda hanya bisa dibaca oleh "
"penerima yang dituju. Kami tidak menyimpan informasi identitas pribadi (PII)"
" pengirim di database kami. Alamat IP hanya dicatat secara terenkripsi untuk"
" mencegah penyalahgunaan sistem (spam) dan akan dihapus secara otomatis "
"dalam periode tertentu."
msgstr ""
"Security is the core foundation of CurhatBox. We use advanced encryption "
"protocols to ensure that your messages can only be read by the intended "
"recipient. We do not store personally identifiable information (PII) of the "
"sender in our database. IP addresses are only recorded encrypted to prevent "
"system abuse (spam) and will be deleted automatically within a certain "
"period."

msgid "Bisakah penerima mengetahui lokasi atau identitas saya?"
msgstr "Can the recipient know my location or identity?"

msgid ""
"Tidak. Lokasi geografis presisi Anda tidak akan pernah dibagikan. Penerima "
"hanya akan melihat 'Sender Hints' berupa tipe perangkat dan browser (misal: "
"iPhone, Safari) untuk memberikan konteks dasar tanpa membahayakan privasi "
"Anda. Identitas asli Anda terkunci rapat di sistem internal kami."
msgstr ""
"No. Your precise geographic location will never be shared. The recipient "
"will only see 'Sender Hints' in the form of device type and browser (e.g., "
"iPhone, Safari) to provide basic context without endangering your privacy. "
"Your true identity is locked tight in our internal system."

msgid "II. Fitur Pesan Sekali Baca (Self-Destruct)"
msgstr "II. Self-Destruct Message Feature"

msgid "Apa itu mode Self-Destruct?"
msgstr "What is Self-Destruct mode?"

msgid ""
"Mode Self-Destruct atau 'Bom Waktu' adalah fitur premium yang memungkinkan "
"Anda mengirim pesan rahasia yang akan langsung terhapus dari database kami "
"sesaat setelah penerima mengeklik tombol untuk membukanya. Setelah pesan "
"tersebut hancur, tidak ada cara apapun (bahkan oleh tim teknis kami) untuk "
"memulihkannya kembali. Ini adalah jaminan privasi mutlak bagi Anda."
msgstr ""
"Self-Destruct mode or 'Time Bomb' is a premium feature that allows you to "
"send secret messages that will be immediately deleted from our database as "
"soon as the recipient clicks the button to open them. Once the message is "
"destroyed, there is no way (even by our technical team) to recover it. This "
"is a guarantee of absolute privacy for you."

msgid "Apakah penerima masih bisa melakukan screenshot pesan?"
msgstr "Can the recipient still take a screenshot of the message?"

msgid ""
"Meskipun kami mencegah perekaman layar melalui sistem web di beberapa "
"browser, fungsi screenshot bawaan perangkat masih dimungkinkan. Oleh karena "
"itu, kami menyarankan Anda tetap bijak dalam mengirimkan informasi yang "
"sangat sensitif meskipun menggunakan mode sekali baca."
msgstr ""
"Although we prevent screen recording via web systems in some browsers, "
"built-in device screenshot functions are still possible. Therefore, we "
"advise you to remain wise in sending very sensitive information even when "
"using single-read mode."

msgid "III. Layanan & Pengelolaan Akun"
msgstr "III. Service & Account Management"

msgid "Berapa biaya penggunaan CurhatBox?"
msgstr "How much does it cost to use CurhatBox?"

msgid ""
"Layanan dasar CurhatBox adalah GRATIS selamanya. Kami didukung oleh iklan "
"untuk menjaga server tetap menyala. Di masa depan, kami mungkin akan "
"memperkenalkan fitur berlangganan opsional untuk kustomisasi tingkat lanjut,"
" namun fitur utama pengiriman pesan akan selalu gratis bagi semua orang."
msgstr ""
"Basic CurhatBox services are FREE forever. We are supported by ads to keep "
"the server running. In the future, we may introduce optional subscription "
"features for advanced customization, but the main messaging feature will "
"always be free for everyone."

#| msgid "Bagaimana jika saya menerima pesan kasar?"
msgid "Bagaimana jika saya lupa password?"
msgstr "What if I forget my password?"

msgid ""
"Kami menyediakan fitur pemulihan akun melalui alamat email yang Anda "
"daftarkan. Pastikan untuk selalu menggunakan email yang aktif agar Anda "
"tidak kehilangan akses ke dasbor pesan Anda."
msgstr ""
"We provide an account recovery feature via your registered email address. "
"Ensure you always use an active email so you do not lose access to your "
"message dashboard."

msgid "Punya pertanyaan lain?"
msgstr "Have other questions?"

msgid ""
"Jika Anda tidak menemukan jawaban yang dicari, tim kami siap membantu "
"melalui email resmi."
msgstr ""
"If you do not find the answer you are looking for, our team is ready to help"
" via official email."

